nodes.text: Around 3627 BBY, Vice Admiral Dol Narlock of the Galactic Republic was captain of the Republic Navy's dejarik team.

The Republic Navy dejarik team was mentioned in the Codex entry for Vice Admiral Narlock in the 2019 expansion Onslaught to the 2011 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars: The Old Republic by the company BioWare.
